Robert D. Isom Jr.
Executive Compensation
As President at AMERICAN AIRLINES GROUP INC, Robert D. Isom Jr. made $6,552,114 in total compensation.  Of this total $641,306 was received as a salary, $1,176,667 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $4,635,000 was awarded as stock and $99,141 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


