Insider Activity


Individual




Robert D. Isom



Mr. Robert D. Isom is President at American Airlines Group, Inc. and President at American Airlines, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at The Wings Club. Mr. Isom was previously employed as Chief Executive & Operating Officer by US Airways, Inc., Chief Operating Officer & Executive Vice President by US Airways Group, Inc., Chief Restructuring Officer by Ally Financial, Inc., Chief Operating Officer by Residential Capital LLC, SVP-Ground Operations & Airport Customer Services by Northwest Airlines, Inc., Chief Operating Officer & Executive Vice President by America West Airlines, Inc., Chief Operating Officer & Executive Vice President by America West Holdings Corp., and Group Manager by Procter & Gamble Co. He also served on the board at Pinnacle Airlines Corp. and St. Mary's Food Bank Alliance. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Notre Dame and an MBA from the University of Michigan.



